PRIVACY POLICY
Last updated May 15, 2025

Focuz+ is a free app developed by Froylan Almeida that helps users create and organize shopping lists using voice commands. 
Your privacy is important to us, and we want to be clear about how the app works:

ðŸ”’ Data Collection
The app does not collect any personal data.
There is no login, no user tracking, and no external data storage or analytics of any kind.

ðŸŽ¤ Permissions
Focuz+ requests access to your microphone only to convert your voice into text for creating shopping lists.
The app does not access the internet, Bluetooth, camera, location, contacts, or any other device features.
